Package: bdt
Title: R package for calling and retrieving big data analyses performed by Big Data Tools (BDT)
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Fang", "Du", email = "fangdu64@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	person("Ben", "Sherwood", email = "bsherwo2@jhu.edu", role = c("aut", "ths")),
    person("Hongkai", "Ji", email = "hji@jhu.edu", role = c("aut", "ths")))
Description: The bdt R package is to run BDT within R for seamless integration. Under the hood, it simply calls BDT commond line tools and provides a convinient way to retrieve the output results from BDT into R for follow-up analysis.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.2), latticeExtra
License: GPL-2
LazyData: false
